{"tid":326430,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"佢唔記得我生日","createTime":"2017-07-18T03:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-18T12:09:21.000Z","uid":25903,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"72bd8fd4bc4768d09e1a6bb0f63de996a2fccfd9","tid":326430,"uid":25903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T03:56:14.000Z","msg":"同佢差唔多日日whatsapp傾左兩個月<br />\n中間見過一次 雖然只係食個lunch<br />\nwtsapp會講早抖早晨 又叫我快啲訓個啲<br />\n同埋會擔心我 仲有講啲曖昧野<br />\n<br />\n點知佢唔記得我生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n（岩岩識個時有問大家幾時生日）<br />\n生日個日完左之後 我見佢一句生日快樂都無<br />\n好唔開心 跟住就藍剔左佢<br />\n<br />\n宜家過左就黎十日<br />\n佢都無搵過我<br />\n我好想搵返佢 但又好犯賤咁<br />\n佢係咪只係搵我攝時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4cad2f901b3e0b32411e473c41b71300c2ee6d4","tid":326430,"uid":120581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:06:32.000Z","msg":"醒吓啦？"},{"pid":"096f246195174b6993e912919c006b986d0948be","tid":326430,"uid":25903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:26:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醒吓啦？</blockquote><br />\n我都想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c66e38e48a8c004fb2932493c2a15cc006ed4f2","tid":326430,"uid":25903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T04:27:07.000Z","msg":"我都想唔鍾意佢 唔在意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab945d28064eaa100c8491a83459ae001687ccb","tid":326430,"uid":71742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:52:23.000Z","msg":"人火"},{"pid":"26fecb0f1b488e91ba270ed4a3e55c9d43c91c48","tid":326430,"uid":71742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T06:52:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人火</blockquote><br />\n係"},{"pid":"f6254867f0f8dc1cffc49cfb1edf4e09eec0575b","tid":326430,